hopobject.body: I'd like to open a business account medicines and healthcare products regulatory agency linkedin "I'd often have read his part while we were writing or rewriting or improvising, and I have to admit - it's not just that he's just died - I never did it anything like as good as he did. It was always a sort of 'How did he do that then?'. But that's a mark of all good performers. They suddenly take what you hoped were quite reasonably funny lines and it turns them into something more magical."
